  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5278297/" class="title-link">不要躺在马克思的怀里卖萌，应该站在马克思的肩...</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5278297"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2116608/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2116608-34.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2116608/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">辄馨</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-01-22"
      class="main-meta">2012-01-22 22:30:34</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5278297_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  如果我写本科毕业论文的那会看到这本书，我的论文在深度上或许能提升两个档次。当然，当时这本书的中文版也还没有出，估计出了我也不一定会去看。 虽然我当时也曾考虑过要把马克思放到古典人类学脉络当中去，但对于庞大的老马，始终找不到合适的切入口，于是只好放弃了这个宏大...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5278297/#comments">(31回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">27有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5278297_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5278297_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1626223">
        

